    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This vehicle is a diamond in the rough that\u2019s ready for some dedicated TLC! While it definitely shows its age and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its best, it offers a fantastic foundation for anyone who loves a good fixer-upper. Grab this opportunity to own a vehicle with great potential at a price that leaves plenty of room for your personal touch!",
